= Introduction =

This directory hosts all the files needed by oscar-packager to automatically
package switcher for OSCAR. For more details, please install oscar-packager
and run the 'man oscar-packager' command.

= Notes about OSCAR RPM for switcher =

Note that the env-switcher RPM is "noarch", so you don't need any SRPM.

If you make any changes, please contact the main developer of env-switcher:
http://env-switcher.sf.net/ - Jeff Squyres <jsquyres@lam-mpi.org>.
